alerts.headline: Cold Weather Advisory issued December 14 at 10:01PM CST until December 15 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Nashville TN
alerts.description:
* WHAT...Temperatures will be in the low teens to single digits
through Monday morning with low single digit wind chill values.

* WHERE...All of Middle Tennessee.

* WHEN...Until noon CST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Wind chill values can lead to hypothermia with prolonged
exposure.
